'''Yawurute''' (izina mu [[giturukiya]] ''yoğurt'')

Ku bantu bafata ibyo biribwa [[Ibikomoka ku mata|bikomoka ku mata]] birimo nka [[foromaje]], yawurute, abakoreweho igenzura basanze bafite amahirwe macye yo gufatwa n’indwara z’umutima kurusha abatarigeze bafata ibyo biribwa. Umubiri ukenera kandi ibikomoka ku mata : [[amata]], yawurute, foromaje ibi bitanga karisiyumu ikomeza amagufa , poroteyine kimwe na vitamini A,B,C.
